			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Use ReCon command \"oe COL_Butcher\" or use the debugbook to go to the Colony Morgue\r\n- Enable godmode with \"god\"\r\n- Attack Chop, the butcher\r\n- After a certain amount of turns, Chop will say this AD. You can Ctrl+Shift+End to skip combat turns and speed up the process."
				},
